**/diseases_160_0.6b_po_cot/**
**/diseases_160_0.6b_po_no_cot/**
**/geo_160_0.6b_po_cot/**
**/geo_160_0.6b_po_no_cot/**
**/objects_158_0.6b_po_cot/**
**/objects_158_0.6b_po_no_cot/**

